{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "原初之力 第24章 5-6 女神的王牌",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "尽管五龙恢复了原初之力，\\n众人却也明白这样仍然无法与泽诺斯对抗。\\n伊莉雅则向烦恼的众人提出了方法。\\n汇聚巫女之力，“创造属于自己的世界”。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "奈迪犹怎么样了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "嗯，看起来好多了。\\n不过动用原初之力所带来的\\n影响似乎还是很大……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "回到勒福克斯旧址的话，\\n应该能找到一两处尚存的建筑。\\n等他能动身的时候我们再去那里吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "奈迪犹动用的力量原本是要\\n在五龙合为一体之时\\n才能使用的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "他还能保留意识\\n已经是不幸中的万幸。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "毕竟当初是我提议说要恢复五龙的\\n原初之力，事情没有演变到\\n最糟糕的情况让我也松了一口气。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "不过我们最终恢复了原初之力。\\n姑且还算是圆满收场了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "是啊，五龙恢复了原初之力，\\n这的确是件值得高兴的事情……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "但那原初之力——准确来说是\\n获得了原初之力的巴哈姆特毁灭之力，\\n真的能够再次使出来吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "也许是有些难度……\\n毕竟奈迪犹稍微使用了一下\\n就变成那副惨状了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我应该连使用都成问题吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "如果我们效仿曾经的始祖，\\n合为一体成为毁灭之力的容器，\\n或许还有可能。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我才不要那样呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我知道现在不是任性时候……\\n可我真的没法就这样答应……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "因为一旦合体，穆穆就会不复存在对吧？\\n耶梦加得他们也是。\\n这种结果我也不想要看到……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊……\\n而且原初碧龙这样说过。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "即使五龙融合为巴哈姆特，\\n也没能战胜泽诺斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "当时是因为有圣域龙和\\n“起始之龙”所创造的世界，\\n才能将泽诺斯再次封印……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "是啊……圣域龙已经不在了。\\n就算我们采取相同的方法，\\n也有可能无法封印泽诺斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯。\\n所以我认为寄希望于这个方法的话，\\n风险太大了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这的确是合理的判断……\\n但这样一来我们就没有\\n与泽诺斯抗衡的手段了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01",
                "110367_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "现在还不是泄气的时候。\\n我们还有其它手段对付泽诺斯。\\n关键在你的身上，塞西娅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "诶？这是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "不只是你，\\n还有泽娜和席菈，\\n当然也包括我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜&席菈",
            "context": "？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "你的意思是……“巫女”吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没错。\\n我们巫女正是对抗泽诺斯的关键。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "巫女是关键？何出此言？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "泽诺斯的能力是创造世界。\\n因为他能创造出自己想要的世界，\\n所以身在其中的我们才会束手无策。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "与其对抗的手段之一，\\n是毁灭他的世界。\\n就像这次奈迪犹用巴哈姆特的力量一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "而另一个手段就是——\\n“创造属于我们的世界”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "创、创造世界！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我们也创造一个由我们掌控的世界，\\n然后用这个世界来覆盖泽诺斯的世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "你、你说得倒简单，\\n可这难道不是一件相当不得了的事吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这当然不是一件容易的事情，\\n但我们有成功的可能性。\\n贝维特这次就向我们证明了这一点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "贝维特哥哥吗……\\n啊！原来是这样！\\n贝维特哥哥是刻印之器，也就是说——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没错，和我们巫女一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "当然，\\n我们和贝维特在力量的大小上\\n有着相当大的差距。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "但若是贝维特在本质上与我们并无不同，\\n那我们也应该可以像他那样创造世界！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "你还真是语出惊人啊……\\n该说……不愧是女神吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "呵呵。我好歹也被称为神了，\\n不试着创造一两个世界怎么行呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "可、可是伊莉雅，\\n创造世界这种事，我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "单靠我们自己肯定是\\n不足以创造世界的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "所以我们要像五龙融合为\\n巴哈姆特那样，\\n将巫女的力量也汇聚起来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "汇集巫女之力，\\n创造世界……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没错。召集巫女并汇集力量……\\n我们与泽诺斯对抗的王牌——\\n正是“信赖”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_11_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}